{"tid":638450,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊六月去北九州八日七夜，有咩要注意?_?","createTime":"2018-04-22T17:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T19:36:23.000Z","uid":64894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e273886443ed313cc2e3ebd3fb29c2b9c35a0909","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:24:09.000Z","msg":"其實想各位巴打幫下眼，評下小弟既北九州行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，順手推介下野食同睇下有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一日：香港 &rarr; 福岡<br />\n17:15福岡機場落機－去拉麵競技場食<br />\n<br />\n第二日：福岡 &rarr; 佐賀 &rarr; 武雄<br />\n10點出發去佐賀－行2個鐘頭佐嘉神社－食季樂－下晝2點幾到武雄－單車遊圖書館－溫泉老街掃街－夜晚睇螢火蟲－武雄溫泉<br />\n<br />\n第三日：武雄 &rarr; 佐世保<br />\n下晝一點到九十九島－水族館－五番街－石岳展望台<br />\n<br />\n第四日：佐世保 &rarr; 長崎<br />\n10點幾到四町商店街－長崎原爆資料館－平和公園－稻佐山－思案橋<br />\n<br />\n第五日：長崎<br />\n大浦天主堂－軍艦島－Glover garden（食旧自由亭）－出島－觀光通商店街（食吉宗茶碗蒸）<br />\n<br />\n第六日：長崎 &rarr; 別府 <br />\n中午到別府地獄（食別府冷麵）－竹瓦溫泉/小路－夜晚食酒店會席料理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第七日：別府 &rarr; 由布院 &rarr; 天神<br />\n朝早9點到由布院－金麟湖－湯之坪街道掃街－5點幾到天神－夜晚食海風土/燒肉多牛－天神地下街－宵夜食小金屋台<br />\n<br />\n第八日：天神 &rarr; 香港<br />\n水鏡天滿宮－警固神社－搭12點幾機走<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f85efc7960d0d67159a174297c24d56e725791","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea4e03a83a3df95ff0aa36c0d4be16d5ecf5fdd","tid":638450,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"睇我po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352456b724eab2b55223937133e731db2b605fec","tid":638450,"uid":24432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩先係九州返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73127d2218860c5bc42fe28d4e5c5a47188bd04","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea4e03a83a3df95ff0aa36c0d4be16d5ecf5fdd","tid":638450,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"睇我po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"巴打行程太chur唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4eccee522653d42570772fcfb42708a48f08627","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352456b724eab2b55223937133e731db2b605fec","tid":638450,"uid":24432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩先係九州返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d807418f6f578e044fd4f33f42c6e35c8714244","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73127d2218860c5bc42fe28d4e5c5a47188bd04","tid":638450,"uid":64894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ea4e03a83a3df95ff0aa36c0d4be16d5ecf5fdd","tid":638450,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"睇我po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"巴打行程太chur唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji